it later, it's called a

00:04:40.120 --> 00:04:42.590
Nonlinear Non-scaling
Fixed-Field Alternating

00:04:42.590 --> 00:04:45.510
Gradient Accelerator.

00:04:45.510 --> 00:04:47.780
Now the other thing which
relates to real particle

00:04:47.780 --> 00:04:50.790
accelerators is the
power source.

00:04:50.790 --> 00:04:54.000
Accelerators based on this Van
de Graaff principle were

00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:56.320
